Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.81,0:04:18.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is that...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.43,0:04:20.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's Raizo's voice.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.39,0:04:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! The ninja?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.31,0:04:29.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Ninja!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.95,0:04:33.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Ya-hoo! Where's the ninja?!\N--Ninja! Ninja!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.45,0:04:41.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here we are.\NHe-{\i1}gara{\i0} is the ninja, Raizo.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:41.33,0:04:43.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There you are, Cat Viper!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.00,0:04:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You! Why didn't you just \Nhand me over to them?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.97,0:04:52.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Everyone that brought me food here...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:52.43,0:04:54.74,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...was injured!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.76,0:04:58.62,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,They told me the country is okay,\Nbut is it true?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.64,0:05:06.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If it's a lie, I, Raizo, will hate you!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.61,0:05:15.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.20,0:05:23.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's nothing like we expected!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:28.63,0:05:36.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}"A Red Stone!\NA Guide to the One Piece!"{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:40.89,0:05:45.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey! What in the world has happened,\NCat Viper?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:45.35,0:05:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me, Raizo.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:47.61,0:05:55.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We had no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.79,0:06:04.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's a disappointment.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.04,0:06:07.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--His face is huge!\N--Doesn't seem like a fast runner!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.13,0:06:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--Is that Raizo?\N--I can't accept a ninja like that!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.09,0:06:20.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I don't think you guys are from this country!\NWho are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.56,0:06:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Raizo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.31,0:06:28.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Kin'emon! Kanjuro! Momonosuke-{\i1}sama{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:28.11,0:06:31.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,--I'm glad that you're okay!\N--We're glad you're okay too!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.78,0:06:39.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Raizo!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.37,0:06:43.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry to keep you waiting, Raizo!\NI'll unchain you now!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.96,0:06:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:57.09,0:07:05.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's your problem, you bastards?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.27,0:07:12.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Look at this place.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.07,0:07:19.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.82,0:07:26.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The crest of the Kozuki Family!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.37,0:07:28.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The same as Kin'emon's!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.79,0:07:35.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That crest has existed for centuries.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.42,0:07:38.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that stone is...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.43,0:07:44.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I've never seen it in such a color.\NDeep red...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:44.02,0:07:51.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, it's a Ponegliff.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:51.98,0:07:57.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We know you-{\i1}gara{\i0}, Nico Robin.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:57.82,0:08:03.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I heard the Ohara people \Ncan read those letters.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:03.58,0:08:11.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So you two know about Ohara.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.78,0:08:48.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here, this proves that you're\Na scholar. Take this, Robin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.54,0:08:50.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm happy for you, Robin.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.21,0:08:53.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Congratulations!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.92,0:08:58.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen, Robin. You must understand well\Nwhat it means to be an archaeologist.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.84,0:09:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, Professor Clover!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.78,0:09:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why is that Ponegliff red?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.91,0:09:33.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,None of the Ponegliffs I've ever seen\Nwere that color.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.83,0:09:41.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It has a different purpose.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.51,0:09:43.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can you read it?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.43,0:09:45.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, may I?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.01,0:09:54.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Of course, you may.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.99,0:10:06.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What's wrong with you guys?\NWhy are you staring hard at me like that?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.74,0:10:08.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you really a ninja?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:08.95,0:10:11.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How insolent! Who are you?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.41,0:10:13.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We haven't introduced them to you yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:13.75,0:10:18.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Raizo, they're the Straw Hats.\NThey're pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.50,0:10:19.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Pirates?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:20.00,0:10:24.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,If you're a real ninja, throw a {\i1}shuriken{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.59,0:10:27.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Meditate under a waterfall!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:27.60,0:10:31.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Say "Nin" and use ninja powers!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.06,0:10:32.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna see the Earth Escape Technique!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.98,0:10:34.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I want the fire version!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.85,0:10:36.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, the water version!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:36.48,0:10:38.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Such rapid-fire requests!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.48,0:10:42.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show us your ninja powers already!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:42.53,0:10:45.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Why do you pirates want to see it so badly?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.28,0:10:50.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's not because we're pirates.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.12,0:10:52.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Super{\i0}!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.95,0:11:00.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All boys like ninjas!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.22,0:11:16.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That makes me blush.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:16.06,0:11:20.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, have you ever gone out\Nwith a female ninja?!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.52,0:11:24.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Train your jumping ability\Nby jumping over a bamboo shoot every day!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.53,0:11:28.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show me the Shadow Clone Technique.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.16,0:11:32.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hide in the ceiling and \Nget stabbed by a spear.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.58,0:11:34.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Fly in the sky with a cloth parachute!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.70,0:11:36.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Summon a giant frog!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.00,0:11:40.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hold a scroll in your \Nmouth and say "Nin-nin"!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:41.00,0:11:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Raizo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.04,0:11:42.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Raizo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.92,0:11:44.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Raizo!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.09,0:11:45.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hurry up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:45.46,0:11:47.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Just do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.80,0:11:54.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Show us ninja powers!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.39,0:11:56.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.60,0:12:01.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Stop imposing your damn dreams on me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.36,0:12:07.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We ninja don't say things like "Nin-nin"!\NThe ninja in your heads are all fantasies!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.24,0:12:10.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.82,0:12:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Th-They don't say that?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:13.20,0:12:18.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Then, what makes you a ninja?!\NIt can't be your physique!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.25,0:12:24.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right. With this physique,\NI can't even attract female ninjas...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.21,0:12:28.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.05,0:12:33.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Listen! It takes a quiet and \Ntough mind to be a master ninja!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.80,0:12:37.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We're supposed to be living in the shadows.\NWe can't show off our techniques.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.81,0:12:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ninjutsu{\i0} is not entertainment...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.42,0:13:13.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ninpo{\i0} - Smoke Escape Technique!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.09,0:13:13.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,H...
Dialogue: 0,0:13:14.01,0:13:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He disappeared!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:16.14,0:13:18.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.77,0:13:22.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Where did he go?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.40,0:13:28.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't disappear!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.40,0:13:29.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm here.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.69,0:13:35.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.20,0:13:36.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And here too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.78,0:13:38.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.08,0:13:39.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Here too!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.50,0:13:42.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! He's got doubles?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.04,0:13:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Could it be...?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.88,0:13:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ninpo{\i0} - Shadow Clone Technique!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.09,0:13:49.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:49.92,0:13:54.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's this? Can you catch me?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.22,0:14:00.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:00.06,0:14:02.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I got you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.85,0:14:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,How's this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.52,0:14:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Ninpo{\i0} - Body Replacement Technique!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.16,0:14:20.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,He's unexpectedly agile!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.79,0:14:23.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Did you doubt I was really a ninja?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.66,0:14:26.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Flower Shuriken!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:26.50,0:14:34.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,SHINOBI
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.97,0:14:42.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Never popular with girls\Nbut still an invincible ninja!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.10,0:14:47.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Raizo of the Mist is now...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.40,0:14:54.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...here before your eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:54.78,0:14:56.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The ninja's so cool!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.91,0:14:59.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Raizo!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.91,0:15:07.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nin! Nin!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.86,0:15:33.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nin-nin! You're unbelievable!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.94,0:15:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nin-nin! Being a ninja isn't about how you look\Nbut about your mind! Nin-nin!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.82,0:15:47.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Can I become a ninja\Nif I train myself a lot?! Nin-nin!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.54,0:15:52.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Nin-nin!\NI wanna see more {\i1}ninjutsu{\i0}! Nin-nin!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.63,0:16:00.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Cut the Nin-nin crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.68,0:16:03.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You already saw my {\i1}ninjutsu{\i0} accidentally.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.72,0:16:05.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Accidentally?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.39,0:16:07.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I know you did them for us!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:07.52,0:16:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,These fools...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.49,0:17:05.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Are you guys crying?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:05.41,0:17:10.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Don't be silly!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:10.50,0:17:17.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Men from the Land of Wano don't cry!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.96,0:17:24.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,It's just...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.72,0:17:32.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...it wasn't like this when I arrived here!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.94,0:17:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The city and the river were both beautiful!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.28,0:17:45.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The streets were bustling
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.83,0:17:49.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and people were living their lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.12,0:17:50.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And the whole country...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.75,0:17:58.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,...was full of energy!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.99,0:19:11.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Damn those Minks!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.99,0:19:15.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What they did was so rash!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:15.54,0:19:23.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I will work as hard as I can to avenge you!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.76,0:19:25.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,So forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.72,0:19:33.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Forgive me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:53.41,0:19:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you-{\i1}gara{\i0} guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.21,0:20:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Seems like the deciphering of the stone is done!\NCome back into the whale!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:04.09,0:20:05.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What do you think, Nami?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.97,0:20:10.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Is this what's written on the Ponegliff?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:10.05,0:20:14.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I can draw a nautical \Nchart based on this!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:14.10,0:20:19.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,We can pinpoint the location of something,\NRobin!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.48,0:20:26.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That red stone is called a Road Ponegliff!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:26.36,0:20:32.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,All the tough guys of the sea are \Nsearching for the end of the Grand Line,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.33,0:20:40.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,and that stone is a guide to get there!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:41.33,0:20:44.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The Whale Forest is considered sacred\Nbecause of it
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.92,0:20:48.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,so it needs to be protected by us Guardians!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.97,0:20:52.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The end of the Grand Line...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.89,0:20:57.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,You mean, a guide to the \Nlast island - Raftel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.81,0:20:59.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's right!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.14,0:21:00.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.44,0:21:01.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,However...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.48,0:21:03.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Raftel?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.36,0:21:07.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the goal!\NTo become King of the Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.86,0:21:15.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Finally, we can get there!\NThe last island - Raftel!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:18.25,0:21:23.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's the island the flower pops mentioned!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:23.13,0:21:26.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Does it say where Raftel is?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:26.30,0:21:31.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Wait, wait, don't jump to conclusions!\NHear me out. You see...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.93,0:21:37.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,There are four of those red stones - the Road Ponegliffs\Nin the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.68,0:21:41.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,What?! Does it mean there are four Raftels?!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.19,0:21:46.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,No, there aren't! Let him finish first!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.52,0:21:54.52,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That stone must indicate the location of\Nsome unknown spot but it's not Raftel.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.70,0:22:04.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The other three Road Ponegliffs all indicate\Ndifferent locations in the same manner.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:04.25,0:22:10.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,When you learn where those locations are\Nand connect those four points on a map,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:10.26,0:22:18.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,those lines will cross at the center!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:22.39,0:22:24.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,That's where the last island is.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:24.40,0:22:32.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,Only the King of the Pirates and his crew \Nhave reached it in all these centuries!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.57,0:22:41.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,And that's Raftel!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.18,0:23:02.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,The last island - Raftel!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:10.73,0:23:14.97,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The mystery of the Ponegliffs\Nthat Robin is searching for comes to light!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:14.99,0:23:17.97,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}When the conflict among the Four Emperors\Nwho are trying to get to Raftel{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.99,0:23:20.19,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}and the deep connection between the
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.21,0:23:23.18,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,Kozuki Clan,\Nincluding Momonosuke, and the Ponegliffs are revealed,{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.20,0:23:26.56,Italics,,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Luffy will learn the samurais' great sorrow!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:23:26.58,0:23:27.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,On the next episode of One Piece!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.92,0:23:31.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,“The Secret of the Land of Wano!\NThe Kozuki Family and the Ponegliffs!”
Dialogue: 0,0:23:31.21,0:23:39.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,I'm gonna be the King of the Pirates!
